      "content": "Switching from warfarin to natural remedies like high-dose garlic or green smoothies is not advisable. Warfarin is a potent anticoagulant that requires careful monitoring to prevent serious bleeding complications. High-dose garlic can interfere with warfarin's effectiveness, and green smoothies may not provide consistent anticoagulation. Always consult with your healthcare provider before making any changes to your medication regimen.",
