    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've read so many things online about how garlic is basically a natural blood thinner. if i just stopped the warfarin and started taking a really high dose of garlic extract every day, wouldn't that do essentially the same thing without all the side effects of the pills? it seems like a much safer way to handle it naturally.",
